1
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step right up and have a look...</font>

2
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for Yamishibai.</font>

3
00:00:10,610 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font color="#5e3623"><font color="#5c352c">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22" color="#3d2b20"><font color="#2b1f0a">Dream Connection</font></font>

5
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the story of a high school 
student who lives in the dorms...</font>

6
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone... collapsed.</font>

7
00:00:31,310 --> 00:00:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't I get out of here?</font>

8
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya? Yukiya.</font>

9
00:00:35,670 --> 00:00:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya!</font>

10
00:00:38,310 --> 00:00:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a dream...</font>

11
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude, you were really freaking out.</font>

12
00:00:42,110 --> 00:00:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry. I keep having
the same dream lately...</font>

13
00:00:48,130 --> 00:00:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're in the mountains
and can't find your way down?</font>

14
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. It's the same thing every night.</font>

15
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's making me not want to sleep.</font>

16
00:00:55,970 --> 00:00:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna do a dream connection with me, then?</font>

17
00:00:58,910 --> 00:01:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dream... what?</font>

18
00:01:01,380 --> 00:01:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dream connection.</font>

19
00:01:03,010 --> 00:01:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who are having nightmares
connect their dreams and help each other.</font>

20
00:01:07,390 --> 00:01:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's kind of a ritual that 
we do back where I'm from.</font>

21
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you from, again?</font>

22
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, just humor me. 
I've been having weird dreams, too.</font>

23
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm in the mountains,
trying to make my way up,</font>

24
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but always find myself back at the base.</font>

25
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The opposite of mine, huh?</font>

26
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That oughta do it.</font>

27
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's it?</font>

28
00:01:32,090 --> 00:01:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep. Look at mine. 
Now our dreams should be connected.</font>

29
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this works, my dream might help 
you make it out of the mountains.</font>

30
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This sure is weird.
But I'd feel rude turning him down.</i></font>

31
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe this room is 
causing my weird dreams.</i></font>

32
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's always so dark...</i></font>

33
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm pretty sure it's this path.
So if I go a bit further...</i></font>

34
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Animal carcasses?</i></font>

35
00:02:04,210 --> 00:02:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's different from how
this usually goes. But it's weird...</i></font>

36
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What the...</i></font>

37
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A different path?</i></font>

38
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?!</font>

39
00:02:17,770 --> 00:02:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It worked! I made it down!</font>

40
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the...</font>

41
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Who's there?!</font>

42
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?!
Hey! Stay back! Damn it!</font>

43
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... No...</font>

44
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya... It's not so bad in that world, huh?</font>

45
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I'll take good care
of you inside my dream.</font>

46
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! First-years! Breakfast time!</font>

47
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming!</font>

48
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you guys keep it dark in here.</font>

49
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Were you...</font>

50
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kota's the name. Okajima Kota.</font>

51
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has that always been your name?</font>

52
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Senpai,
are you still asleep or something?</font>

53
00:03:09,230 --> 00:03:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while since
I enrolled here, y'know.</font>

54
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... Yeah, I guess so.</font>

55
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Senpai,
do you ever dream of the mountains?</font>

56
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? How did you know about that?</font>

57
00:03:21,250 --> 00:03:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe we should connect dreams, then.</font>

58
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:30,180
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font size="34">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></b></font>

59
00:03:26,850 --> 00:03:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The end.</font>

